de.patricklammers.vorlesungsplan.app.actionbar

Class SimpleMenu

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.patricklammers.vorlesungsplan.app.actionbar.SimpleMenu
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Menu

    public class SimpleMenu
extends Object
implements Menu
    A really dumb implementation of the Menu interface, that's only useful for our actionbar-compat purposes. See com.android.internal.view.menu.MenuBuilder in AOSP for a more complete implementation.
